# Key Idea: Use LLM Only When Necessary

Instead of every step calling the model, the system separates tasks into:

| Task Type             | Tool Used         |
| --------------------- | ----------------- |
| Deterministic parsing | Python            |
| Notebook AST analysis | Python            |
| Pipeline generation   | Rules + templates |
| Complex reasoning     | LLM               |

